If we just do POST instead of GET everywhere inside Piwik, that's going the opposite way of rest. E.g. using POST to get information doesn't make sense in HTTP.
> If we just do POST instead of GET everywhere inside Piwik, that's going the opposite way of rest. E.g. using POST to get information doesn't make sense in HTTP.

